
If you do not yet know what LaTeX is all about, have a look at a short
introduction to LaTeX: 
   http://www.latex-project.org/intro.html

The (Not So) Short Introduction to LaTeX2e, by Tobias Oetiker et al is
a good beginner's tutorial:
   http://ctan.tug.org/tex-archive/info/lshort/english/lshort.pdf 

There are a number of translations available: 
   ftp://ctan.tug.org/tex-archive/info/lshort/portuguese/

